<title>HONG KONG: COSCO (Hong Kong) mandates US$80 mln loan.</title>
<headline>COSCO (Hong Kong) mandates US$80 mln loan.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1996-09-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>COSCO (Hong Kong) Group Ltd has mandated Credit Lyonnais Hong Kong to arrange a US$80 million amortising loan facility, bankers said said on Friday.</p>
<p>They said the facility has a final maturity of five years with no puts or calls option.</p>
<p>No further details are available yet.</p>
<p>COSCO (Hong Kong) is wholly owned by China Ocean Shipping (Group) Co.</p>
<p>COSCO (Hong Kong) in turn owns about 64 percent of Hong Kong listed COSCO Pacific Ltd.</p>
<p>--Hong Kong Newsroom (852) 2847 4039</p>
